{"tid":1343734,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[22-07-2019]股市直擊+波神信眾區","createTime":"2019-07-21T19:21:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T13:58:35.000Z","uid":49083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c8d02cfe0d432bbd3f818fed089cb43d4164ab2c","tid":1343734,"uid":49083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:21:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=dsIiHtEXBJA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdsIiHtEXBJA&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcv3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=49f918e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=dsIiHtEXBJA</a><br />\nI want the rebels to know I'm alive. That I'm in District 8, where the Capitol just bombed a hospital filled with unarmed men, women and children. There will be no survivors. If you think for one second that the Capitol will ever treat us fairly you are lying to yourself. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Because we know who there are and what they do.</span> This is what they do, and we must fight back! I have a message for President Snow. You can torture us, bomb us, burn our districts to the ground. But do you see that? <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Fire is catching! And if we burn, you burn with us!</span>"},{"pid":"a48950f46a8f5a376739ab72a583cf4464b82ad0","tid":1343734,"uid":49083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:23:51.000Z","msg":"我從來都係最怕死果個<br />\n但我就係怕死，我先走出黎<br />\n<br />\n橫死掂死，點解要死得不明不白"},{"pid":"6075262ec30527b00e551b007c1bc9ddb731be50","tid":1343734,"uid":56752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:26:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd25bfd5c18e6b75a72d0de6cae4d6f0b0a8264","tid":1343734,"uid":43469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:39:38.000Z","msg":"D7PCBC警🐶🐮💩"},{"pid":"14159654495b3888e39b3d4f9b37ca54f7e41a32","tid":1343734,"uid